<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<h2 id="Decision-Tress">Decision Tress<a class="anchor-link" href="#Decision-Tress">&#182;</a></h2><p><strong>Udacity: Intro to Machine Learning</strong></p>
<p>Chapter 4</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> Since required dependencies are not available, this is just a code snippet for now (instead of executing in cell blocks).</p>
<p><strong>Finding Accuracy:</strong></p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class="prompt input_prompt">
</div>
<div class="inner_cell">
<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">sys</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">class_vis</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">prettyPicture</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">prep_terrain_data</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">makeTerrainData</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">sklearn</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">tree</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">sklearn.metrics</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">accuracy_score</span>

<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="kn">as</span> <span class="nn">np</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">pylab</span> <span class="kn">as</span> <span class="nn">pl</span>

<span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">features_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_test</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">makeTerrainData</span><span class="p">()</span>



<span class="c1">#################################################################################</span>


<span class="c1">########################## DECISION TREE #################################</span>

<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">classify</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">):</span>

    <span class="c1">### your code goes here--should return a trained decision tree classifer</span>
    <span class="n">X</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">features_train</span>
    <span class="n">Y</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span>
    <span class="n">clf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tree</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DecisionTreeClassifier</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">clf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">clf</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fit</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">X</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">Y</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">clf</span>

<span class="c1">#### your code goes here</span>
<span class="n">clf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">classify</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="c1"># ask classifier to predict</span>
<span class="n">labels_pred</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">clf</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">predict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_test</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">acc</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">accuracy_score</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">labels_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_pred</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="c1">### be sure to compute the accuracy on the test set</span>



<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">submitAccuracies</span><span class="p">():</span>
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s2">&quot;acc&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">acc</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)}</span>
</pre></div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class="prompt input_prompt">
</div>
<div class="inner_cell">
<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">

<div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class="prompt input_prompt">
</div>
<div class="inner_cell">
<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p><strong>Minimum Samples (2 and 50):</strong></p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class="prompt input_prompt">
</div>
<div class="inner_cell">
<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">sys</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">class_vis</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">prettyPicture</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">prep_terrain_data</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">makeTerrainData</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">sklearn</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">tree</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">matplotlib.pyplot</span> <span class="kn">as</span> <span class="nn">plt</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="kn">as</span> <span class="nn">np</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">pylab</span> <span class="kn">as</span> <span class="nn">pl</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">sklearn.metrics</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">accuracy_score</span>

<span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">features_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_test</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">makeTerrainData</span><span class="p">()</span>



<span class="c1">########################## DECISION TREE #################################</span>


<span class="c1">### your code goes here--now create 2 decision tree classifiers,</span>
<span class="c1">### one with min_samples_split=2 and one with min_samples_split=50</span>
<span class="c1">### compute the accuracies on the testing data and store</span>
<span class="c1">### the accuracy numbers to acc_min_samples_split_2 and</span>
<span class="c1">### acc_min_samples_split_50, respectively</span>
<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">classify</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">min_samples</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">):</span>

    <span class="c1">### your code goes here--should return a trained decision tree classifer</span>
    <span class="n">X</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">features_train</span>
    <span class="n">Y</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span>
    <span class="n">clf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tree</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DecisionTreeClassifier</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">min_samples_split</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">min_samples</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">clf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">clf</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fit</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">X</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">Y</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">clf</span>

<span class="n">clf_2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">classify</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">clf_50</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">classify</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">50</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">labels_pred_2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">clf_2</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">predict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_test</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">labels_pred_50</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">clf_50</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">predict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_test</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">acc_min_samples_split_2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">accuracy_score</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">labels_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_pred_2</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">acc_min_samples_split_50</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">accuracy_score</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">labels_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_pred_50</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">submitAccuracies</span><span class="p">():</span>
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s2">&quot;acc_min_samples_split_2&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">acc_min_samples_split_2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">),</span>
          <span class="s2">&quot;acc_min_samples_split_50&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">acc_min_samples_split_50</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)}</span>
</pre></div>

</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<h2 id="DT-Mini-Project">DT Mini Project<a class="anchor-link" href="#DT-Mini-Project">&#182;</a></h2><p>Email classification.<br>
Starter skeleton code is <a href="https://github.com/udacity/ud120-projects/blob/master/decision_tree/dt_author_id.py">here</a></p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="cell border-box-sizing code_cell rendered">
<div class="input">
<div class="prompt input_prompt">In&nbsp;[12]:</div>
<div class="inner_cell">
    <div class="input_area">
<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="ch">#!/usr/bin/python</span>

<span class="sd">&quot;&quot;&quot; </span>
<span class="sd">    This is the code to accompany the Lesson 2 (SVM) mini-project.</span>

<span class="sd">    Use a SVM to identify emails from the Enron corpus by their authors:    </span>
<span class="sd">    Sara has label 0</span>
<span class="sd">    Chris has label 1</span>
<span class="sd">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
    
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">sys</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">time</span> <span class="k">import</span> <span class="n">time</span>
<span class="n">sys</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">path</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;../tools/&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">email_preprocess</span> <span class="k">import</span> <span class="n">preprocess</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">sklearn</span> <span class="k">import</span> <span class="n">tree</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">sklearn.metrics</span> <span class="k">import</span> <span class="n">accuracy_score</span>


<span class="c1">### features_train and features_test are the features for the training</span>
<span class="c1">### and testing datasets, respectively</span>
<span class="c1">### labels_train and labels_test are the corresponding item labels</span>
<span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">features_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_test</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">preprocess</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># 10 is percentile</span>




<span class="c1">#########################################################</span>
<span class="c1">### your code goes here ###</span>
<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">classify</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">min_samples</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">):</span>

    <span class="c1">### your code goes here--should return a trained decision tree classifer</span>
    <span class="n">X</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">features_train</span>
    <span class="n">Y</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span>
    <span class="n">clf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tree</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DecisionTreeClassifier</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">min_samples_split</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">min_samples</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="c1"># train the classifier</span>
    <span class="n">t0</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">time</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">clf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">clf</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fit</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">X</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">Y</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Decision Tree Training time: &quot;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">time</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">t0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s2">&quot; s&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>    
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">clf</span>

<span class="n">clf_40</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">classify</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">40</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1"># predict</span>
<span class="n">t0</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">time</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">labels_pred_40</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">clf_40</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">predict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_test</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Decision Tree Prediction time: &quot;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">time</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">t0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s2">&quot; s&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1"># accuracy</span>
<span class="n">acc_min_samples_split_40</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">accuracy_score</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">labels_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_pred_40</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Decision Tree Predicted labels: &quot;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">labels_pred_40</span><span class="p">)))</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Decision Tree Accuracy: &quot;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">accuracy_score</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">labels_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_pred_40</span><span class="p">)))</span>

<span class="c1">#########################################################</span>
</pre></div>

</div>
</div>

<div class="cell border-box-sizing code_cell rendered">
<div class="input">

<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="ch">#!/usr/bin/python</span>

<span class="sd">&quot;&quot;&quot; </span>
<span class="sd">    This is the code to accompany the Lesson 2 (SVM) mini-project.</span>

<span class="sd">    Use a SVM to identify emails from the Enron corpus by their authors:    </span>
<span class="sd">    Sara has label 0</span>
<span class="sd">    Chris has label 1</span>
<span class="sd">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
    
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">sys</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">time</span> <span class="k">import</span> <span class="n">time</span>
<span class="n">sys</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">path</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;../tools/&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">email_preprocess</span> <span class="k">import</span> <span class="n">preprocess</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">sklearn</span> <span class="k">import</span> <span class="n">tree</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">sklearn.metrics</span> <span class="k">import</span> <span class="n">accuracy_score</span>


<span class="c1">### features_train and features_test are the features for the training</span>
<span class="c1">### and testing datasets, respectively</span>
<span class="c1">### labels_train and labels_test are the corresponding item labels</span>
<span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">features_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_test</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">preprocess</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">percentile</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>




<span class="c1">#########################################################</span>
<span class="c1">### your code goes here ###</span>
<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">classify</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">min_samples</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">):</span>

    <span class="c1">### your code goes here--should return a trained decision tree classifer</span>
    <span class="n">X</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">features_train</span>
    <span class="n">Y</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span>
    <span class="n">clf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tree</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DecisionTreeClassifier</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">min_samples_split</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">min_samples</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="c1"># train the classifier</span>
    <span class="n">t0</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">time</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">clf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">clf</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fit</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">X</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">Y</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Decision Tree Training time: &quot;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">time</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">t0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s2">&quot; s&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>    
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">clf</span>

<span class="n">clf_40</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">classify</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_train</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">40</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1"># predict</span>
<span class="n">t0</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">time</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">labels_pred_40</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">clf_40</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">predict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">features_test</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Decision Tree Prediction time: &quot;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">time</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">t0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s2">&quot; s&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1"># accuracy</span>
<span class="n">acc_min_samples_split_40</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">accuracy_score</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">labels_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_pred_40</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Decision Tree Predicted labels: &quot;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">labels_pred_40</span><span class="p">)))</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Decision Tree Accuracy: &quot;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">accuracy_score</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">labels_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">labels_pred_40</span><span class="p">)))</span>

<span class="c1">#########################################################</span>
</pre></div>
